|             | support standby mode on p1020   |             |           |                                           |
| 	      | p2020                           |             |           |                                           |
|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| QLINUX-8954 | no "Suspend to RAM and standby" | Open        | LSDK-1803 |                                           |
|             | in menuconfig for DPAA platform |             |           |                                           |
|             |                                 |             |           |                                           |
|             |                                 |             |           |                                           |
|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
